{"tid":42132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急尋】26歲女子黃麗慧天水圍失蹤","createTime":"2016-12-16T12:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T08:07:17.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"faaa79f7c51d9b685efab23abddd8876b087c654","tid":42132,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161216/large/1481886981_b8d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161216%2Flarge%2F1481886981_b8d0.jpg&h=0a880d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n26歲女子黃麗慧前日下午離開其位於天恆邨的住所後便告失蹤，其家人於翌日向警方報案。黃女身高約1.6米，體重約45公斤，瘦身材，尖面型，黃皮膚及蓄啡長直髮。她最後露面時身穿灰色外套，綠色長裙，白色運動鞋及攜有白色手袋。她後頸、右腳踝及右上臂有紋身圖案。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲任何人如有該失蹤女子的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 3112或6273 5787或電郵至rmpu-ntn-1@police.gov.hk與新界北總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161216/56057087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161216%2F56057087&d=u2h3VxJJ04AYXVCnABRvTXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=092eb3b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161216%2F56057087&h=a02cd1c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161216/56057087</a>"},{"pid":"958b1e37b228e29d221fcb0d1e567c1756be9f12","tid":42132,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"連登有冇偵探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab3e484448b264bc2c4a1bebaa337ab878554f7","tid":42132,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"化到咁，落左妝點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9419cb049471293640d47be99486b22f2603f95","tid":42132,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":